      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You transform the target, rapidly updating its components and mechanisms to modern design standards for the spell’s duration. If the target has the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.Nrf6oy9pJwcEmryP.JournalEntryPage.nXkFsyxk7Vybdn7G#archaic]{Archaic} weapon special property, it temporarily loses that property. If the target’s item level is lower than your caster level, the target’s hardness temporarily increases by 3, and it gains 5 Temporary Hit Points that disappear when the spell ends. If the target is a suit of armor, it immediately gains and activates its environment protections.</p>"
